title: Sanjjanaa's special celebration with Upendra
text:
Pretty lass Sanjjanaa turned a year older last week. While there were many people who wished the actress and even celebrate with her, Sanjjanna will perhaps cherish one celebration the most.
The actress brought in her birthday with Real Star Upendra and his wife, Priyanka Upendra. She cut the cake in their presence an then went on to release the music of her forthcoming film, Ramleela.
Sanjjanaa uploaded the following picture, with the caption, "Celebrated mybirthday with @realupendra @ipriyanka_Up & happy tat they released the song of ourmostawaited #RamLeela"
